        <p>After leading the team through problem statement, critical path, persona building, and rapid sketching exercises, we aligned on the designs we needed to create a prototype to test with seven Groups members and staff personnel. Overall, our testing sessions helped us validate and invalidate some key assumptions (which ultimately saved us a ton of time!), and we landed on some helpful insights moving forward:</p>

        <div class="heading-lockup">
          <div class="heading-lockup__item">
            <h5 class="heading-lockup__subheading">Insight 1</h5>
            <h4 class="heading-lockup__heading">Remove as much friction as possible in the sign up flow to ensure members complete it and get the care they need</h4>
          </div>

          <div class="heading-lockup__item">
