        <p>After getting the cadence and relevance down, my next step was to add visual design elements to the articles. I was handed plain Word docs, and in MVP-land I could've just split all the copy into &lt;p&gt; tags and headings and called it a day. But I felt a duty to add illustrations and typography design for readability and user delight, and incorporated the visual branding I developed for the app. This way, the articles felt not only part of the app experience, but tailored and thoughtful ‚Äì to convey to members that the team who built this app cares about them and their recovery.</p>

