        <h2 class="article__subheader">Conclusion</h2>
        <p>Overall, the MVP was a success in that it set Groups Recover Together up to further fulfill their mission to bring care to more people throughout the country. The features we designed and built were also in service to measuring their three main metrics ‚Äì attendance, abstinence, and retention ‚Äì to determine whether supporting remote treatment is beneficial not only to their members, but to their business as a whole. If according to the data, remote-treatment continues to be just as, if not more effective, than in-person treatment, then the team will continue to iterate on their app to further explore ways to give members a truly unique and empowering digital experience throughout their recovery.</p>
